  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (MRL 3)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. This package re-evaluates COU1 at Model Risk Level 3 following an upward revision of the decision consequence to Critical, reflecting updated clinical risk data. Seven factors are fully assessed and meet their required levels. Three factors are declared not-assessed on the basis that they are considered beyond the current project scope; however, no concrete justification for scope exclusion is provided.",
