      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study was conducted on the baseline pump geometry (coarse: 2.1 M cells, medium: 5.8 M cells, fine: 14.3 M cells). GCI for the normalized index of hemolysis was 3.2%, below the 5% threshold. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
