      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental conditions (flow rates 2.5–6 L/min, rotational speeds 2000–3500 RPM) are fully documented with reported measurement uncertainties. Simulated boundary conditions were set to match experimental values within stated tolerances. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative metric (e.g., E% or U_val) must be computed and compared against validation acceptance threshold.",
      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index predictions were compared against FDA experimental data at all five operating points. Mean absolute percentage error was 8.4% and all predictions fell within experimental uncertainty bands. The acceptance criterion RH < 1 was satisfied at the worst-case operating condition. Achieved level 3 meets required level 3."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
