      "acceptanceCriteria": "The QoIs used in validation must be the same as, or directly traceable to, the QoIs used in the COU decision.",
      "rationale": "The normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) and relative hemolysis index (RH) computed in validation activities are identical to the QoIs specified in the COU acceptance criterion. No transformation or surrogate metric is introduced. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the validation activities to the COU",
