      "rationale": "Model form uncertainty was considered beyond the scope of the present assessment. Alternative turbulence closures and hemolysis constitutive models were not systematically evaluated. The team considers this a lower-priority item given prior published studies, but no formal evidence was gathered to support this position within the current package."
