      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and boundary condition inputs must be documented with sources and uncertainty estimates.",
      "rationale": "Blood viscosity (3.5 mPa·s), density (1056 kg/m³), and red blood cell fragility parameters are drawn from published literature with cited uncertainty ranges. Pump geometry dimensions are taken from the FDA benchmark CAD files with documented tolerances. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test samples",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
