      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test samples must be representative of the device population and sample size must support statistical comparison.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data were collected from three independent laboratories using five pump specimens each, providing adequate sample diversity. Blood analog fluid properties were controlled within ASTM specifications. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
