      "acceptanceCriteria": "Input parameters used in the simulation must be equivalent to those present in the validation experiment within documented tolerances.",
      "rationale": "Dimensional equivalency between the CAD model and physical test specimens was confirmed via coordinate measurement machine data provided in the FDA benchmark dataset. Flow rate and rotational speed set-points match within 1% of experimental values. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
