    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the seven assessed factors collectively provide sufficient evidence to support the COU decision at MRL 3. Three factors (Numerical solver error, Use error, Model form) were not assessed and are acknowledged as beyond the current project scope. The team judged that the assessed factors provide adequate compensating evidence; however, no formal compensating analysis was performed to substantiate the acceptability of the unassessed factors at MRL 3.",
